There are mating faces in Tolerance GS of Fastening Part.
CMME6512:Error(s) occurred in Weld Check. Please confirm the Weld 3DA.
System error occurred in the process of checking individual fastening parts has external links.
CMME6367:Re-open PUB document which may have been updated in background. Or execute pub-division because PUB document may not synchronize latest WRK modification.
The value of Weight property is illegal.
CMME6375:Individual fastening Part is not created.
CMME6347:There is any Standard Part is not placed by command.
CMME6543:There is a derivation which doesn't link to any view part.
CMME6545:Hide/Show status in VM is different from one defined in Management Information.
